warmup(long).Description: Warm up the browser process. Allows the browser application to pre-initialize itself in the background. Significantly speeds up URL opening in the browser. This is asynchronous and can be called several times.

ClassDesc: Class to communicate with a @B_android#support#customtabs#CustomTabsService_E@ and create @B_android#support#customtabs#CustomTabsSession_E@ from it.
